<h2 id=3D"infenterprisebeneficiarymanagementv1-POST/beneficiaries/summary">=
<span>POST /<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">beneficiaries/summary</sp=
an></span></h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves all <span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">benefi=
ciaries </span>that the user is entitled to and only return accounts / bene=
ficiaries.&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span><span class=3D"status-macro =
aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">FEB 26</span> enhance to support last used=
, "NEW" flag and the additional fields required for payment.&nbsp;</span></=
span></p>
