<h1 id=3D"infenterprisebeneficiarymanagementv1-Capability:Retrievingabenefi=
ciarydetail"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability:<sp=
an class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> Retrieving a beneficiary detail</span>=
</strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"infenterprisebeneficiarymanagementv1-GET/beneficiaries/{id}"><spa=
n>GET /<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">beneficiaries/{id}</span></spa=
n></h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves <span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">beneficiar=
y detail </span>that the user is entitled to and is ACTIVE.</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span><span class=3D"status-macro =
aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">FEB 26</span> </span>supports capability t=
o retrieve payment template (embedded in beneficiary), new flag and last us=
ed.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><br></p>
