<h1 id=3D"infenterprisebeneficiarymanagementv1-Capability:Updatebeneficiary=
"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability: Update benefi=
ciary&nbsp;</strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"infenterprisebeneficiarymanagementv1-PUT/beneficiaries/{id}">PUT =
/beneficiaries/{id}</h2>
<p>This endpoint updates the details of the beneficiary / account provided =
in request body.</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span><span class=3D"status-macro =
aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">FEB 26</span> enhance to support payment t=
emplate, last used and "NEW" flag. The API should enforce a behaviour of st=
ate transition from "ON_HOLD" to "ACTIVE" and rejects invalid state transit=
ion. &nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
