></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Must be a GUID (Globally unique message identifier). Consumer generated =
message identifier for correlation purposes. e.g. This is used to group tog=
ether a number of downstream API/provider calls initiated from a single API=
 call, comprising a business transaction. This MUST be propagated</p></td>
