></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The organisation the caller is operating in.</p><p>Available values : WP=
AC, SGB, BSA, BOM, BTPL, UBS, VIRG, RAMS, BAS, WNZL</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
