></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The originating consumption channel invoking the API (eg. Partner, Staff=
, Customer). Note that an API consuming another API should pass the value s=
upplied by the calling application. Further information regarding this head=
er can be found at<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.west=
pac.com.au/x/cbH-B" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/=
x/cbH-B</a>.</p><p><em>Available values</em><span>&nbsp;</span>: Partner, P=
ublic, Staff, Customer, Prospect, Other</p></td>
